{"tid":1378164,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"禁止狗隻入境可唔可行？","createTime":"2019-07-28T15:19:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T17:20:43.000Z","uid":57490,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2b8371b9f79f351953a3c70df0e26d821f216e2a","tid":1378164,"uid":57490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T15:19:58.000Z","msg":"經過咗兩個月<br />\n警察濫用暴力鍾意執行私刑喺唔止香港人見到<br />\n其他國家都知道 我地可唔可以同其他國家講<br />\n例如香港人常去嘅日本台灣禁止佢地入境<br />\n以免佢地去旅行嘅時候又控制唔到情緒打其他國家嘅人？<br />\n不過當然係要禁佢全家 即喺老婆仔女父母呢d直系親屬<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b709f25d1592a52646e40af236e48ec75dfdf989","tid":1378164,"uid":57490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:20:43.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}